info.title: ERP Reborn
info.description: > **It's not just an ordinary ERP** ERP Reborn merupakan proyek sistem Enterprise Resource Planning yang digunakan oleh PT QDC Technologies (diinisiasi sejak akhir tahun 2020). Main Features : 1. Multiple Users 2. Multiple Companies, Regions, & Branches 3. Multiple Base Currencies & Transaction Currencies 4. Multiple Underlying Document References 5. Convert File Attachments To Thumbnails Automatically 6. SQL Injection Threat Prevention For Some Implemented APIsEndFragment
